{
  "stem": "13623.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We got to a point, I don't know where we were at, rumors were that they bombed the railroad ahead of us.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They let us all get off the train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The guards surrounded the train, and we were just sitting and waiting for-- to see what else they're going to tell us to do.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At this point, I was just with some of the kids, some of the people that I befriended in the camps and some of the people that I helped when I worked in the kitchen that I used to bring them food.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We sort of tried to stay together.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We were, for-- for the better part of a day, loose where we can stretch our legs, and we were surrounded, the train was surrounded, and we were able to move about.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] As I-- at that point, my bread was long gone.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't get fed anymore, and we were just hungry.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "As hungry can be.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I-- I spotted a discarded tube of toothpaste, and I picked it up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I really didn't know why I picked it up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Maybe I was curious to see what it was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I put it in my pocket.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We were given orders to get back onto the train, and we are continuing our journey.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We don't have any food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We don't have any water.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "My mouth is dry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "My-- my tongue is-- I don't know how, I got-- I found my-- my-- that discarded, it was a discarded tube, but it still had a little bit of toothpaste in it.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I squeezed a little bit of toothpaste-- toothpaste on my tip of my finger and, if I licked it, it sort of created saliva in my mouth.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
